Some of the DVD's froze from time to time, but since Candy is from 1979, I think is still in good quality.  It was worth every penny.  Loved that it took it me back to my beautiful childhood.  I laughed and cried with Candy again and again.
This is a wonderful series!! It brought me back to my childhood days with beautiful memories and I am now sharing this with my wonderful daughter. She loves it as well.

I received my first copy, and didn't even test it, when i gifted it to my mom 6 months later, we found out some discs were defective. I contacted the seller and they immediately sent another full series, this time it all worked! Thank you soo much!

It is a fair reproduction, i was under the impression i was getting originals, but they are fair reproductions.  The quality is fair, for the price, it should be better. I have been wanting this seriea for a long time though, about 20 years, so seeking th and finding them is an accomplishment in itself! I watched the series as a child, in a different country, so just finding it has been marvelous!
